**Carbon Cycle:** Plants absorb carbon from the atmosphere, and store it in their bodies. When plants die, decomposers break down the plant and release its carbon back into the atmosphere. Positive feedback loop: A change in an ecosystem that causes an effect reinforcing the first change.
